<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Continuar</title>
<style>
  :root{
    --verde: #04834D;
    --verde-escuro: #04532F;
    --creme: #FAF8F2;
    --texto: #16241E;
    --texto-suave: #5C6B64;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0;}
  body{
    font-family:'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
    background:var(--creme);
    color:var(--texto);
    min-height:100vh;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    padding:24px;
  }
  .card{
    background:#fff;
    border-radius:16px;
    box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(10,31,51,0.10);
    max-width:420px;
    width:100%;
    padding:40px 32px;
    text-align:center;
  }
  .icon{
    width:60px; height:60px;
    border-radius:50%;
    background:rgba(4,131,77,0.1);
    color:var(--verde);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    font-size:28px;
    margin:0 auto 20px;
  }
  h1{
    font-size:20px;
    margin-bottom:10px;
  }
  p{
    font-size:14px;
    color:var(--texto-suave);
    margin-bottom:28px;
    line-height:1.5;
  }
  .btn{
    display:inline-block;
    width:100%;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--verde), var(--verde-escuro));
    color:#fff;
    border:none;
    padding:15px 20px;
    border-radius:10px;
    font-size:16px;
    font-weight:600;
    cursor:pointer;
    text-decoration:none;
  }
  .btn:hover{opacity:0.95;}
  .footnote{
    font-size:11px;
    color:#9AA6A0;
    margin-top:18px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="icon">✓</div>
    <h1>Tudo pronto</h1>
    <p>Clique no botão abaixo para continuar.</p>
    <a class="btn" href="https://appsave.online/cl/i/ex2o4d">Continuar</a>
    <div class="footnote">Você será redirecionado em uma nova etapa.</div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
